00:16:25,535 --> 00:16:26,856
No, Desheng.

293
00:16:28,935 --> 00:16:30,055
It's not your fault.

294
00:16:30,096 --> 00:16:31,935
I destroyed my own son.

295
00:16:32,096 --> 00:16:32,976
It's not your fault.

296
00:16:34,775 --> 00:16:35,655
It's not your fault.

297
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,704
(Defendant)
The People's Procuratorate

298
00:16:43,704 --> 00:16:45,560
of Pingchuan County,
Dongjiang Province charges

299
00:16:45,944 --> 00:16:49,815
that Zheng Zhiqiang's group
committed 22 crimes,

300
00:16:50,295 --> 00:16:52,736
involving over 170,000 yuan.

301
00:16:53,616 --> 00:16:57,136
Zhou Xiaohu's gang of five

302
00:16:57,295 --> 00:17:01,295
(committed 43 highway crimes,
including forced towing,)

303
00:17:01,616 --> 00:17:04,535
(extortion, and robbery.)

304
00:17:05,055 --> 00:17:07,016
(The amount involved was 370,000 yuan.)

305
00:17:07,736 --> 00:17:08,815
(The court finds)

306
00:17:09,216 --> 00:17:11,775
(that defendant
Zheng Zhiqiang and others)

307
00:17:11,936 --> 00:17:16,656
(stole a truck on the suburban roads
of Yuehai, Pingchuan County)

308
00:17:16,976 --> 00:17:18,615
(and stabbed Tan with a knife.)

309
00:17:19,176 --> 00:17:24,375
According to Article 150, 134, and 64

310
00:17:24,575 --> 00:17:25,896
of the Criminal Law

311
00:17:26,135 --> 00:17:27,855
of the People's Republic of China

312
00:17:28,095 --> 00:17:29,736
which took effect on January 1, 1980,

313
00:17:30,176 --> 00:17:30,976
the verdict is

314
00:17:31,736 --> 00:17:36,696
that defendant Zheng Zhiqiang,
guilty of robbery and injury,

315
00:17:36,976 --> 00:17:39,535
is sentenced
to six years of imprisonment,

316
00:17:39,815 --> 00:17:41,720
deprivation of political rights
for three years,

317
00:17:41,855 --> 00:17:44,256
(and confiscation
of all personal property.)

318
00:17:45,095 --> 00:17:48,896
(Defendant Wang Wu is sentenced
to six years of imprisonment,)

319
00:17:49,256 --> 00:17:51,256
(deprivation of political rights
for three years,)

320
00:17:51,448 --> 00:17:53,696
(and confiscation
of all personal property.)

321
00:17:54,176 --> 00:17:58,335
(Defendant Qian Dazhuang is sentenced
to six years of imprisonment,)

322
00:17:58,456 --> 00:18:00,504
(deprivation of political rights
for three years,)

323
00:18:00,855 --> 00:18:03,295
(and confiscation
of all personal property.)

324
00:18:04,176 --> 00:18:08,375
(Defendants Zhou Xiaohu
and Zhou Xiaolong, guilty of robbery)

325
00:18:08,615 --> 00:18:09,335
(and injury,)

326
00:18:09,535 --> 00:18:11,535
(are sentenced to life imprisonment,)

327
00:18:11,832 --> 00:18:13,592
(deprivation of political rights
for life,)

328
00:18:13,896 --> 00:18:16,536
(Super Dog Restaurant)
(and confiscation of all personal property.)

329
00:18:17,055 --> 00:18:20,135
(Defendant Yang Xiaohai,
not guilty of robbery.)

330
00:18:20,656 --> 00:18:22,216
(Guilty of mob fighting)

331
00:18:22,456 --> 00:18:24,568
(and participation
in forced high-price hauling.)

332
00:18:24,656 --> 00:18:27,216
(Sentenced
to eight months' imprisonment.)

333
00:18:27,936 --> 00:18:31,855
(Defendant Chen Guilin is sentenced
to ten years' imprisonment,)

334
00:18:32,152 --> 00:18:34,104
(deprivation of political rights
for four years.)

335
00:18:40,375 --> 00:18:41,016
Granny.

336
00:18:42,496 --> 00:18:43,535
I'm sorry.

337
00:18:44,375 --> 00:18:45,896
I didn't make stop him.

338
00:18:48,416 --> 00:18:51,095
Eight months isn't long.

339
00:18:54,176 --> 00:18:57,295
Xiaohai needs a lesson.

340
00:18:58,736 --> 00:18:59,775
I've decided

341
00:19:01,456 --> 00:19:02,736
to bring you to the town office.

342
00:19:04,184 --> 00:19:05,240
I'll take care of you.

343
00:19:07,416 --> 00:19:08,535
I'm not going.

344
00:19:08,896 --> 00:19:09,736
Why not?

345
00:19:10,575 --> 00:19:11,375
The food there

346
00:19:14,696 --> 00:19:15,736
isn't good.

347
00:19:19,055 --> 00:19:20,176
You're just making excuses.

348
00:19:21,736 --> 00:19:25,335
Then, I'll let people to come in shifts.

349
00:19:25,736 --> 00:19:27,176
I'll also visit you often.

350
00:19:28,696 --> 00:19:29,696
Take care of yourself.

351
00:19:30,295 --> 00:19:31,375
I'm here for everything.

352
00:19:51,375 --> 00:19:52,016
It's okay.

353
00:19:52,815 --> 00:19:53,416
It's okay.

354
00:20:15,575 --> 00:20:16,216
Hai.

355
00:20:17,736 --> 00:20:19,016
What will the world be like

356
00:20:19,055 --> 00:20:20,736
when I get out?

357
00:21:04,535 --> 00:21:05,016
Desheng.

358
00:21:13,736 --> 00:21:14,416
Sister-in-law.

359
00:21:33,375 --> 00:21:34,135
Zheng Decheng!

360
00:21:34,375 --> 00:21:35,176
How dare you come?

361
00:21:35,216 --> 00:21:36,135
Get out!

362
00:21:36,416 --> 00:21:37,335
Give me my son back!

363
00:21:37,375 --> 00:21:38,696
S-Shut up.

364
00:21:39,256 --> 00:21:40,976
Go b-back.

365
00:21:44,456 --> 00:21:46,615
You've been crying all day.

366
00:21:46,815 --> 00:21:48,016
Stop making a scene.

367
00:21:49,815 --> 00:21:51,256
So what if Zhiqiang's in prison?

368
00:21:52,216 --> 00:21:52,936
I'm telling you.

369
00:21:53,416 --> 00:21:55,615
We shouldn't have come here.

370
00:22:06,535 --> 00:22:08,016
You see this old house?

371
00:22:09,696 --> 00:22:11,016
There's even your height marked.

372
00:22:12,575 --> 00:22:15,775
Living here, I sometimes dream of Mom.

373
00:22:19,016 --> 00:22:20,855
Our hometown is gone.

374
00:22:22,416 --> 00:22:24,095
We followed you here.

375
00:22:26,896 --> 00:22:29,535
A-And you sent Zhiqiang to jail.

376
00:22:32,375 --> 00:22:32,936
Desheng.

377
00:22:33,815 --> 00:22:35,896
Did I send him in?

378
00:22:37,016 --> 00:22:38,216
He committed a crime.

379
00:22:38,855 --> 00:22:41,815
He must be punished by law.

380
00:22:42,416 --> 00:22:44,256
When I came here that night,

381
00:22:44,535 --> 00:22:45,936
you shouldn't have covered for him.

382
00:22:46,256 --> 00:22:47,775
You should've told me the truth.

383
00:22:47,976 --> 00:22:50,135
He's your nephew!

384
00:22:51,135 --> 00:22:51,736
Let me ask you.

385
00:22:52,736 --> 00:22:54,256
Since we came to Yuehai,

386
00:22:54,736 --> 00:22:56,256
have I ever asked you for anything?

387
00:22:58,256 --> 00:23:01,656
We came here for a better life.

388
00:23:02,575 --> 00:23:04,696
Did we get any help from you?

389
00:23:05,176 --> 00:23:08,375
No. Never!

390
00:23:10,375 --> 00:23:11,535
Zhiqiang's fate is bad.

391
00:23:11,696 --> 00:23:12,575
He deserves it.

392
00:23:13,016 --> 00:23:17,055
If it was 10,000-yuan household,
you'd do everything you could to help.

393
00:23:17,656 --> 00:23:18,736
Zhiqiang was right.

394
00:23:19,375 --> 00:23:21,368
Y-You're just...

395
00:23:22,488 --> 00:23:24,855
A 'monkey' secretary.

396
00:24:31,055 --> 00:24:31,696
Mr. Zheng.

397
00:24:36,416 --> 00:24:37,335
Why are you here?

398
00:24:40,855 --> 00:24:42,976
I-I came to report to you.

399
00:24:44,535 --> 00:24:45,575
Look at you.

400
00:24:46,736 --> 00:24:48,295
I climbed all the way up here

401
00:24:48,896 --> 00:24:50,535
just to be alone.

402
00:24:51,135 --> 00:24:53,176
And you climbed up to report.

403
00:24:53,696 --> 00:24:55,216
Trying to dodge me?

404
00:24:55,736 --> 00:24:56,696
You wish!

405
00:24:57,815 --> 00:24:59,256
I should've brought my camera

406
00:24:59,456 --> 00:25:00,976
to take you a photo.

407
00:25:01,696 --> 00:25:02,696
A secretary

408
00:25:02,976 --> 00:25:04,575
drinks this much during work hours.

409
00:25:04,815 --> 00:25:05,855
Is that proper?

410
00:25:14,135 --> 00:25:14,815
My fault.

411
00:25:16,055 --> 00:25:17,135
You can report now.

412
00:25:18,416 --> 00:25:20,815
I went to Yang Village and Wang Village,

413
00:25:21,896 --> 00:25:25,135
visited all the families
of the sentenced guys,

414
00:25:25,535 --> 00:25:27,815
and recorded their needs.

415
00:25:29,055 --> 00:25:29,575
Good.

416
00:25:31,456 --> 00:25:32,896
I also visited Zheng Desheng.

417
00:25:47,936 --> 00:25:52,176
So you also think
I'm a 'monkey' secretary?

418
00:25:52,896 --> 00:25:53,656
'Monkey' secretary?

419
00:26:05,176 --> 00:26:06,696
Desheng is barely literate.

420
00:26:08,095 --> 00:26:09,736
But I think he's right.

421
00:26:10,295 --> 00:26:11,656
I am indeed a 'monkey' secretary.

422
00:26:13,176 --> 00:26:15,295
Yuehai needs money to develop.

423
00:26:15,928 --> 00:26:16,984
Where is the money from?

424
00:26:17,736 --> 00:26:18,256
'Monkeys'.

425
00:26:18,896 --> 00:26:19,696
The roads.

426
00:26:20,295 --> 00:26:21,216
The houses.

427
00:26:22,016 --> 00:26:24,815
Everything in Yuehai is built

428
00:26:25,575 --> 00:26:26,135
by 'monkeys'.

429
00:26:27,128 --> 00:26:28,216
City construction fees.

430
00:26:28,896 --> 00:26:29,775
Seven-up, eight-down.

431
00:26:30,295 --> 00:26:30,976
Binhai Road.

432
00:26:31,855 --> 00:26:32,656
I was disciplined.

433
00:26:34,264 --> 00:26:35,815
I went to the leaders again and again.

434
00:26:36,135 --> 00:26:37,456
I offended every cadre.

435
00:26:37,496 --> 00:26:38,335
Who did I do it for?

436
00:26:38,775 --> 00:26:39,375
'Monkeys'.

437
00:26:40,256 --> 00:26:43,855
I care for nobody but 'monkeys'.

438
00:26:44,632 --> 00:26:46,335
If I'm not a 'monkey' secretary,
what am I?

439
00:27:01,176 --> 00:27:01,775
Ms. Li.

440
00:27:06,055 --> 00:27:07,335
I didn't think about others.

441
00:27:09,656 --> 00:27:10,736
Maybe I did.

442
00:27:14,375 --> 00:27:17,575
But I felt they only needed enough
to eat and drink.

443
00:27:21,855 --> 00:27:22,976
I never thought it through.

444
00:27:24,135 --> 00:27:26,295
I never seriously thought

445
00:27:27,375 --> 00:27:28,256
about their desires

446
00:27:29,736 --> 00:27:30,656
and development.

447
00:27:31,976 --> 00:27:33,496
All I cared about were the 'monkeys'.

448
00:27:42,736 --> 00:27:43,936
I'm a secretary.

449
00:27:44,696 --> 00:27:46,976
But when my nephew committed a crime,

450
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:48,375
and went to jail,

451
00:27:50,335 --> 00:27:51,295
I couldn't do a thing.

452
00:27:52,535 --> 00:27:53,095
Mr. Zheng.

453
00:27:53,335 --> 00:27:54,656
It has nothing to do with you.

454
00:27:55,256 --> 00:27:57,016
They weren't sent in by you.

455
00:27:57,815 --> 00:27:58,736
That may be true.

456
00:28:00,176 --> 00:28:02,135
But I should've
paid attention to them earlier.

457
00:28:03,216 --> 00:28:03,815
Mr. Zheng.

458
00:28:04,775 --> 00:28:05,896
Since we build the city,

459
00:28:06,936 --> 00:28:09,295
you've paid great attention
to the people.

460
00:28:09,696 --> 00:28:11,575
You fought for job opportunities

461
00:28:11,936 --> 00:28:12,815
and quotas for them.

462
00:28:13,335 --> 00:28:16,216
The town government even
gives them monthly subsidies.

463
00:28:16,656 --> 00:28:18,535
Zheng Zhiqiang is an individual case.

464
00:28:18,575 --> 00:28:20,016
It's not a group issue.

465
00:28:20,575 --> 00:28:23,775
Yuehai has never been a place
just for 'monkeys'.

466
00:28:27,416 --> 00:28:28,896
We still haven't done enough.

467
00:28:30,135 --> 00:28:31,535
They went down the wrong path

468
00:28:32,055 --> 00:28:34,176
because they were poor
and had no guidance.

469
00:28:35,016 --> 00:28:37,656
We must speed up development

470
00:28:38,575 --> 00:28:40,256
to narrow the wealth gap.

471
00:28:40,656 --> 00:28:43,135
If you think that way,
you're being too impatient.

472
00:28:43,456 --> 00:28:46,696
Our city has developed very rapidly
since its founding.

473
00:28:47,416 --> 00:28:48,896
In the process of development,

474
00:28:49,095 --> 00:28:51,335
problems are inevitable.

475
00:28:52,016 --> 00:28:56,896
As a secretary, you should be thinking
about the path forward,

476
00:28:57,135 --> 00:28:59,496
not blaming yourself over one person.

477
00:29:11,535 --> 00:29:12,055
So...

478
00:29:14,775 --> 00:29:17,656
You don't think
I'm a 'monkey' secretary?

479
00:29:20,055 --> 00:29:20,696
Of course not.

480
00:29:22,216 --> 00:29:24,976
People in our position
will always be criticized.

481
00:29:26,416 --> 00:29:28,375
We just need to do what's right.

482
00:29:28,936 --> 00:29:30,375
That's enough.

483
00:29:51,535 --> 00:29:52,176
Mr. Zheng.

484
00:29:53,335 --> 00:29:54,375
Come take a look.

485
00:30:02,896 --> 00:30:03,775
Do you remember?

486
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:06,529
(When you feel sad, watch the sunrise.
It will warm your heart.)

487
00:30:09,575 --> 00:30:10,855
But that's a sunset.

488
00:30:12,815 --> 00:30:13,615
Come on.

489
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:30,488
♪Should we forget yesterday's sorrows♪

490
00:30:30,488 --> 00:30:33,784
♪And the dazed confusion♪

491
00:30:35,032 --> 00:30:37,737
♪Should we let go of♪

492
00:30:37,737 --> 00:30:39,960
♪The stubborn madness♪

493
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:43,128
♪And naive recklessness now♪

494
00:30:44,248 --> 00:30:47,896
♪Those years, those faces♪

495
00:30:49,048 --> 00:30:52,819
♪Those old scars we can't erase♪

496
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:56,516
♪Tears streaming, facing the light♪

497
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:01,650
(Uphold the Four Cardinal Principles,
Persevere with Reform and Opening-up)

498
00:31:06,854 --> 00:31:08,024
(Regulate Traffic Order,
Ensure Road Safety)

499
00:31:08,024 --> 00:31:09,368
(Environmental Protection,
Benefits today and the future)

500
00:31:20,664 --> 00:31:22,136
(Super Dog Restaurant)

501
00:31:22,136 --> 00:31:26,156
♪The road ahead's long,
stumbling all the way♪

502
00:31:26,956 --> 00:31:31,496
♪The wounds we've borne
are medals hidden within♪

503
00:31:31,756 --> 00:31:35,811
♪Standing alone on an open plain♪

504
00:31:36,588 --> 00:31:40,271
♪We gaze at the stars♪

505
00:31:49,135 --> 00:31:50,416
Excuse me.

506
00:31:50,456 --> 00:31:51,216
Coming through.

507
00:31:52,456 --> 00:31:53,256
Thank you.

508
00:31:54,775 --> 00:31:56,416
Good evening, everyone!

509
00:31:56,615 --> 00:31:57,855
- Good evening!
- Good evening!

510
00:31:58,016 --> 00:31:58,855
Thank you.

511
00:32:03,615 --> 00:32:04,456
Today,

512
00:32:04,815 --> 00:32:07,016
we're holding a small lighting ceremony

513
00:32:07,496 --> 00:32:10,416
at this intersection.

514
00:32:11,335 --> 00:32:12,976
This isn't an ordinary intersection.

515
00:32:13,375 --> 00:32:14,855
For Yuehai,

516
00:32:15,256 --> 00:32:18,176
it is a historic one.

517
00:32:18,936 --> 00:32:20,295
It signifies that Yuehai

518
00:32:20,535 --> 00:32:23,335
has entered a new era.

519
00:32:23,535 --> 00:32:25,575
- Great!
- Great!

520
00:32:26,736 --> 00:32:27,976
Is it impressive?

521
00:32:28,016 --> 00:32:29,095
Yes!

522
00:32:29,295 --> 00:32:30,696
Are you happy?

523
00:32:30,775 --> 00:32:31,896
Yes!

524
00:32:32,416 --> 00:32:33,135
Great!

525
00:32:33,256 --> 00:32:33,815
Leader.

526
00:32:34,535 --> 00:32:35,936
What is this thing?

527
00:32:36,456 --> 00:32:37,736
Can't you tell?

528
00:32:38,256 --> 00:32:39,375
Look at the red...

529
00:32:40,016 --> 00:32:41,656
This is called a traffic signal light.

530
00:32:41,855 --> 00:32:42,335
What light?

531
00:32:42,375 --> 00:32:43,375
A traffic signal light.

532
00:32:43,416 --> 00:32:44,976
Do you see the color?

533
00:32:45,016 --> 00:32:46,016
No, Mr. Xie.

534
00:32:46,095 --> 00:32:47,976
Everyone, listen to me.

535
00:32:48,295 --> 00:32:51,216
Its official name is "traffic signal."

536
00:32:51,335 --> 00:32:52,615
Back in 1988,

537
00:32:52,656 --> 00:32:57,615
the Road Traffic Management Regulations
are issued.

538
00:32:57,896 --> 00:33:00,335
Article 9 of Chapter 2 stipulates...

539
00:33:00,496 --> 00:33:01,775
I don't understand.

540
00:33:02,535 --> 00:33:03,696
Too technical.

541
00:33:04,496 --> 00:33:05,736
Simply, it's a traffic light.

542
00:33:05,775 --> 00:33:06,456
Traffic light.

543
00:33:06,456 --> 00:33:06,896
Alright.

544
00:33:07,535 --> 00:33:08,535
You country bumpkins.

545
00:33:08,536 --> 00:33:09,976
Haven't you been to the county town?

546
00:33:10,135 --> 00:33:12,295
They've had these for ages.

547
00:33:12,535 --> 00:33:14,976
How is that black lump a light?

548
00:33:14,976 --> 00:33:15,736
Listen to me.

549
00:33:16,055 --> 00:33:17,216
No rush.

550
00:33:17,375 --> 00:33:18,736
I'll explain it slowly.

551
00:33:18,736 --> 00:33:20,376
- Turn the light on first.
- It's simple.

552
00:33:20,855 --> 00:33:22,375
Okay. Turn the light on.

553
00:33:22,535 --> 00:33:22,936
Yu.

554
00:33:23,375 --> 00:33:24,095
Turn the light on.

555
00:33:24,216 --> 00:33:25,016
Li.

556
00:33:25,335 --> 00:33:26,456
Turn on the red light!

557
00:33:30,016 --> 00:33:31,696
Stop at red.

558
00:33:32,295 --> 00:33:33,936
Stop at red.

559
00:33:33,976 --> 00:33:35,696
Go at green.

