00:33:43,696 --> 00:33:45,456
Go at green.

565
00:33:46,936 --> 00:33:49,055
Watch your step.

566
00:33:51,416 --> 00:33:51,896
Okay?

567
00:33:54,696 --> 00:33:57,535
Hello, I'm the Town Mayor, Li Qiuping.

568
00:33:58,216 --> 00:34:02,135
Yuehai's development
needs everyone's suggestions.

569
00:34:02,295 --> 00:34:04,055
Please leave a message after the beep.

570
00:34:07,095 --> 00:34:10,296
Ms. Li, you could sound a bit warmer.

571
00:34:11,175 --> 00:34:12,655
Smile and show more enthusiasm.

572
00:34:12,976 --> 00:34:13,255
Okay.

573
00:34:13,255 --> 00:34:13,976
Let's try again.

574
00:34:17,735 --> 00:34:20,255
Hello, I'm the Town Mayor, Li Qiuping.

575
00:34:20,936 --> 00:34:24,976
Yuehai's development
needs everyone's suggestions.

576
00:34:25,416 --> 00:34:26,456
Please...

577
00:34:27,055 --> 00:34:29,896
Ms. Li, still not enough warm.

578
00:34:30,055 --> 00:34:31,615
Could you bring a bit more?

579
00:34:34,264 --> 00:34:35,032
What are you doing?

580
00:34:35,615 --> 00:34:36,535
Where did everyone go?

581
00:34:36,695 --> 00:34:39,000
They are all
at the traffic light ceremony.

582
00:34:41,615 --> 00:34:42,175
Mr. Zheng.

583
00:34:42,575 --> 00:34:44,695
If you're free today,
go to the hospital.

584
00:34:45,016 --> 00:34:47,055
I'm not sick. Why go to the hospital?

585
00:34:48,095 --> 00:34:49,016
Just go. You'll see.

586
00:34:50,896 --> 00:34:51,535
Go.

587
00:34:56,816 --> 00:34:57,376
Fine.

588
00:35:00,735 --> 00:35:01,376
Let's try again.

589
00:35:02,648 --> 00:35:03,352
Be enthusiastic.

590
00:35:03,735 --> 00:35:04,376
Okay.

591
00:35:07,576 --> 00:35:12,330
(Emergency)

592
00:35:42,513 --> 00:35:45,175
(Outpatient Department)

593
00:35:45,175 --> 00:35:47,255
Our hospital is finally built. Right?

594
00:35:47,456 --> 00:35:48,655
It's a trial run now.

595
00:35:48,735 --> 00:35:50,735
Why not be the first
to try it ourselves?

596
00:35:50,816 --> 00:35:51,896
The facilities are ready.

597
00:35:51,976 --> 00:35:54,535
We should take better care
of our health.

598
00:35:54,856 --> 00:35:55,735
This is good stuff.

599
00:35:56,535 --> 00:35:59,255
(Injection Room)
Xuemei worked hard to get it.

600
00:35:59,416 --> 00:36:00,336
Everyone has a dose.

601
00:36:00,456 --> 00:36:01,095
No rush.

602
00:36:01,255 --> 00:36:01,655
Okay.

603
00:36:01,936 --> 00:36:02,816
Xie, you haven't said

604
00:36:02,856 --> 00:36:04,095
what this medicine is.

605
00:36:04,135 --> 00:36:05,615
Is it safe to inject?

606
00:36:05,896 --> 00:36:06,840
Even you don't know?

607
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:07,776
A little nervous.

608
00:36:07,776 --> 00:36:08,184
A little.

609
00:36:08,184 --> 00:36:08,896
Immune human...

610
00:36:13,336 --> 00:36:14,376
Well... Protein...

611
00:36:14,615 --> 00:36:15,055
Protein.

612
00:36:15,095 --> 00:36:15,575
Protein.

613
00:36:16,016 --> 00:36:16,856
Yeah. "Lost"...

614
00:36:16,976 --> 00:36:17,735
What protein?

615
00:36:17,816 --> 00:36:18,535
It's "lost"...

616
00:36:18,655 --> 00:36:19,416
"Get lost" protein.

617
00:36:19,535 --> 00:36:20,896
It tells the viruses to get lost.

618
00:36:21,856 --> 00:36:23,456
It's human immunoglobulin.

619
00:36:23,535 --> 00:36:24,535
Boosts your immunity.

620
00:36:24,728 --> 00:36:25,976
Boosts your immunity.

621
00:36:26,055 --> 00:36:26,936
Yes, that's right.

622
00:36:26,976 --> 00:36:28,976
One shot equals eating a hundred eggs.

623
00:36:29,016 --> 00:36:30,456
College grad, wonderful.

624
00:36:30,456 --> 00:36:31,095
Plain talk.

625
00:36:31,095 --> 00:36:32,336
We should study more.

626
00:36:32,456 --> 00:36:32,936
Correct.

627
00:36:32,936 --> 00:36:33,416
Right?

628
00:36:34,376 --> 00:36:35,016
Yes.

629
00:36:35,615 --> 00:36:36,336
Wait.

630
00:36:36,376 --> 00:36:36,896
Don't rush.

631
00:36:36,896 --> 00:36:37,896
Why isn't Lin here?

632
00:36:38,215 --> 00:36:39,055
Lin isn't coming.

633
00:36:39,175 --> 00:36:39,856
I called him.

634
00:36:39,936 --> 00:36:41,144
He said eating eggs is enough.

635
00:36:42,615 --> 00:36:43,615
Still stubborn as ever.

636
00:36:44,016 --> 00:36:44,936
We must trust science.

637
00:36:44,976 --> 00:36:45,655
Leaders,

638
00:36:46,008 --> 00:36:46,735
we can start now.

639
00:36:46,776 --> 00:36:47,856
Okay.

640
00:36:48,016 --> 00:36:48,376
Start.

641
00:36:48,416 --> 00:36:48,816
Okay.

642
00:36:49,776 --> 00:36:51,296
Lin's quite stubborn sometimes.

643
00:36:51,296 --> 00:36:51,976
Please.

644
00:36:53,496 --> 00:36:54,168
Take it easy.

645
00:36:57,255 --> 00:36:57,936
Shots hurt.

646
00:36:57,936 --> 00:36:58,856
Let me take a look.

647
00:36:59,016 --> 00:36:59,816
Just endure it.

648
00:36:59,816 --> 00:37:00,615
It hurts, right?

649
00:37:01,376 --> 00:37:02,095
That's normal.

650
00:37:02,456 --> 00:37:03,376
Don't move!

651
00:37:03,376 --> 00:37:04,055
Seriously?

652
00:37:04,095 --> 00:37:05,296
You've poked so many times!

653
00:37:05,296 --> 00:37:05,896
Sorry.

654
00:37:06,336 --> 00:37:07,296
Call the head nurse.

655
00:37:07,376 --> 00:37:08,255
Look what you did.

656
00:37:08,296 --> 00:37:09,336
Head nurse!

657
00:37:09,496 --> 00:37:09,936
What's up?

658
00:37:09,936 --> 00:37:11,352
Veins are too small. Won't work.

659
00:37:11,615 --> 00:37:12,135
Check it out.

660
00:37:12,175 --> 00:37:12,776
It's okay.

661
00:37:13,575 --> 00:37:14,336
Come here, sweetie.

662
00:37:14,376 --> 00:37:15,336
Let me take a look.

663
00:37:15,376 --> 00:37:15,976
Let me check.

664
00:37:16,255 --> 00:37:17,936
Exactly, kids have thinner veins.

665
00:37:18,776 --> 00:37:19,575
For adults,

666
00:37:19,615 --> 00:37:21,575
we have to pat and pat
to make the veins show.

667
00:37:21,655 --> 00:37:22,456
For kids, not easy.

668
00:37:22,456 --> 00:37:23,416
Head nurse can do it.

669
00:37:24,776 --> 00:37:25,496
Good boy.

670
00:37:25,535 --> 00:37:26,215
See?

671
00:37:26,575 --> 00:37:26,936
Done.

672
00:37:26,936 --> 00:37:27,535
Done.

673
00:37:27,776 --> 00:37:28,856
Learn from her.

674
00:37:29,272 --> 00:37:29,735
It's done.

675
00:37:29,735 --> 00:37:30,376
Exactly.

676
00:37:30,575 --> 00:37:32,135
It's okay.

677
00:37:32,135 --> 00:37:32,735
Sorry.

678
00:37:33,055 --> 00:37:34,655
Liu, handle the rest.

679
00:37:35,135 --> 00:37:36,575
Kids' veins are hard to find.

680
00:37:36,575 --> 00:37:37,255
Absolutely.

681
00:37:37,336 --> 00:37:37,816
Yes.

682
00:37:37,856 --> 00:37:39,336
Mommy, it hurts.

683
00:37:40,344 --> 00:37:41,055
It's swelling up.

684
00:37:41,055 --> 00:37:42,416
Look at this!

685
00:37:42,416 --> 00:37:43,336
Are you professional?

686
00:37:43,376 --> 00:37:44,695
Swelling is serious.

687
00:37:44,856 --> 00:37:45,535
Sorry.

688
00:37:45,535 --> 00:37:46,095
Swelling up.

689
00:37:46,095 --> 00:37:48,016
Sorry. I'll get another nurse to do it.

690
00:37:48,095 --> 00:37:49,255
No need!

691
00:37:49,296 --> 00:37:50,575
Pull it out now! We're leaving.

692
00:37:50,735 --> 00:37:51,215
Let's go.

693
00:37:51,255 --> 00:37:52,095
Pull it out.

694
00:37:52,416 --> 00:37:53,535
He's suffering enough.

695
00:37:53,735 --> 00:37:54,680
We're done here.

696
00:37:54,680 --> 00:37:55,215
Don't watch.

697
00:37:55,215 --> 00:37:56,135
Calm down.

698
00:37:56,296 --> 00:37:58,095
They've switched nurses.

699
00:37:58,816 --> 00:37:59,535
I saw it.

700
00:38:00,016 --> 00:38:01,856
You don't even know
how to give injections.

701
00:38:02,776 --> 00:38:03,856
This place is awful!

702
00:38:03,856 --> 00:38:04,336
I'm sorry.

703
00:38:04,695 --> 00:38:05,376
Don't say that.

704
00:38:05,575 --> 00:38:06,856
Rest for a bit. Calm down.

705
00:38:06,856 --> 00:38:07,575
We'll handle it.

706
00:38:07,735 --> 00:38:08,496
Take a break.

707
00:38:09,255 --> 00:38:09,912
Seriously?

708
00:38:09,912 --> 00:38:10,680
Aren't you a nurse?

709
00:38:10,680 --> 00:38:12,095
His veins are too thin.

710
00:38:14,296 --> 00:38:15,296
It hurts!

711
00:38:15,936 --> 00:38:17,055
Are you giving shots

712
00:38:17,095 --> 00:38:18,255
(Injection Room)
or killing people?

713
00:38:18,655 --> 00:38:19,856
This is way too painful.

714
00:38:23,735 --> 00:38:25,135
Who hired you people?

715
00:38:25,976 --> 00:38:26,896
With skills like this?

716
00:38:27,055 --> 00:38:28,535
Did you even get proper training?

717
00:38:29,095 --> 00:38:30,336
And you dare to give shots?

718
00:38:32,336 --> 00:38:33,695
I'm calling your director

719
00:38:33,856 --> 00:38:34,896
to get you all fired!

720
00:38:40,135 --> 00:38:41,016
Am I dreaming?

721
00:38:42,055 --> 00:38:43,615
I saw Ms. Li lose it.

722
00:38:44,416 --> 00:38:45,016
Xie.

723
00:38:45,016 --> 00:38:46,296
Is that medicine legit?

724
00:38:46,456 --> 00:38:48,896
I think the medicine is fine.

725
00:38:49,615 --> 00:38:50,936
But Ms. Li might not.

726
00:38:51,095 --> 00:38:52,615
Why do I suddenly feel dizzy?

727
00:38:53,615 --> 00:38:54,776
Maybe I should go.

728
00:38:54,816 --> 00:38:56,095
Let's head back.

729
00:38:56,336 --> 00:38:57,376
Wait, Mr. Zheng.

730
00:38:57,456 --> 00:38:58,575
You're next.

731
00:38:58,695 --> 00:38:59,135
Eat eggs.

732
00:38:59,336 --> 00:39:00,175
Yes, eggs will help.

733
00:39:00,896 --> 00:39:01,655
Meng is the next.

734
00:39:02,095 --> 00:39:03,255
I'll see how skilled she is.

735
00:39:04,095 --> 00:39:05,016
Give her a shot first.

736
00:39:05,336 --> 00:39:06,695
Mr. Hailuo, you go first.

737
00:39:07,128 --> 00:39:07,735
(Town Mayor's Office)
You first.

738
00:39:07,896 --> 00:39:08,896
Ms. Li.

739
00:39:09,215 --> 00:39:11,535
The dentist today was so unprofessional.

740
00:39:12,016 --> 00:39:15,095
I want to extract my wisdom tooth,
but he extracted my molar instead!

741
00:39:16,336 --> 00:39:17,856
They charged one yuan to register,

742
00:39:17,936 --> 00:39:19,175
and then kept asking me

743
00:39:19,336 --> 00:39:20,615
why I was uncomfortable.

744
00:39:20,856 --> 00:39:22,535
If I knew the reason,

745
00:39:22,575 --> 00:39:23,575
why would I come there?

746
00:39:23,615 --> 00:39:25,296
Yuehai Hospital is a mess.

747
00:39:25,456 --> 00:39:26,456
I had stomach pain,

748
00:39:26,615 --> 00:39:28,695
and the pharmacy gave me
the wrong medicine!

749
00:39:28,735 --> 00:39:29,456
I want a refund!

750
00:39:29,976 --> 00:39:31,055
I did a bunch of tests.

751
00:39:31,135 --> 00:39:32,248
I went to get the results.

752
00:39:32,248 --> 00:39:34,575
But they told me they lost my sample.

753
00:39:34,655 --> 00:39:35,296
Ms. Li.

754
00:39:35,535 --> 00:39:37,416
I've been taking the medicine
for half a month,

755
00:39:37,735 --> 00:39:40,016
but still sick,
even have diarrhea every day.

756
00:39:40,416 --> 00:39:41,575
Is this a scam?

757
00:39:42,296 --> 00:39:44,416
This hospital feels useless.

758
00:39:44,856 --> 00:39:47,016
At best, they can handle a cold.

759
00:39:47,296 --> 00:39:50,055
For others, we still have
to go to the county or city hospital.

760
00:39:53,336 --> 00:39:54,655
Let's congratulate Cao.

761
00:39:56,336 --> 00:39:56,735
Thanks.

762
00:39:57,135 --> 00:39:57,976
Thank you.

763
00:39:58,016 --> 00:40:00,296
Cao, you should treat us
for your first big story.

764
00:40:00,856 --> 00:40:02,055
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

765
00:40:02,095 --> 00:40:03,735
Okay. No problem.

766
00:40:04,215 --> 00:40:05,496
Soup dumplings, all you can eat.

767
00:40:06,376 --> 00:40:07,735
- That won't do!
- That won't do!

768
00:40:08,095 --> 00:40:09,535
Don't be so stingy, Cao.

769
00:40:09,776 --> 00:40:11,480
When Reporter Du
got his first big story,

770
00:40:11,575 --> 00:40:14,095
he treated us to West Lake vinegar fish
and braised duck.

771
00:40:14,416 --> 00:40:15,856
- Right?
- Exactly!

772
00:40:15,896 --> 00:40:17,255
Well, I can't compete with Mr. Du.

773
00:40:17,936 --> 00:40:18,776
Mr. Du, you're here.

774
00:40:19,575 --> 00:40:20,655
Got reader letters again?

775
00:40:21,135 --> 00:40:21,535
Yes.

776
00:40:21,936 --> 00:40:22,456
Du.

777
00:40:22,896 --> 00:40:23,976
Cao is your junior, right?

778
00:40:24,695 --> 00:40:26,055
He joined later,

779
00:40:26,416 --> 00:40:28,095
but now he's ahead of you.

780
00:40:29,135 --> 00:40:30,255
Step up your game.

781
00:40:30,456 --> 00:40:30,816
Yes.

782
00:40:31,095 --> 00:40:31,896
You're right.

783
00:40:32,016 --> 00:40:32,896
I'll work harder.

784
00:40:33,016 --> 00:40:33,376
No.

785
00:40:33,695 --> 00:40:35,535
Thanks to Mr. Du
helping me check things.

786
00:40:35,672 --> 00:40:36,936
He got me that headline.

787
00:40:36,936 --> 00:40:37,336
No.

788
00:40:37,456 --> 00:40:39,215
Your topic choice was good.

789
00:40:40,896 --> 00:40:41,695
I-I'll get the call.

790
00:40:41,776 --> 00:40:42,336
You continue.

791
00:40:45,095 --> 00:40:46,135
Alright.

792
00:40:46,215 --> 00:40:47,535
Tonight, dinner's on me.

793
00:40:48,055 --> 00:40:49,055
- Great!
- Great!

794
00:40:52,615 --> 00:40:53,144
Hello?

795
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:54,680
Qiuping.

796
00:40:54,896 --> 00:40:57,016
Du Tao, are you free this weekend?

797
00:40:58,392 --> 00:40:59,896
I'd like to treat your mom to dinner.

798
00:41:00,655 --> 00:41:01,976
Okay, I'll arrange it.

799
00:41:02,328 --> 00:41:02,816
Good.

800
00:41:03,615 --> 00:41:04,896
Let's say 6 PM then.

801
00:41:04,976 --> 00:41:06,135
Let's go together after work.

802
00:41:06,215 --> 00:41:07,535
- Alright.
- Alright.

803
00:41:08,456 --> 00:41:08,976
Senior.

804
00:41:09,655 --> 00:41:11,535
You should take the Jeep.

805
00:41:11,856 --> 00:41:13,095
Your reporting covers more.

806
00:41:13,135 --> 00:41:13,976
You travel further.

807
00:41:14,376 --> 00:41:15,535
No need. I'm fine.

808
00:41:15,655 --> 00:41:16,135
Thanks.

809
00:41:23,255 --> 00:41:23,936
Qiuping.

810
00:41:25,416 --> 00:41:26,175
Need my help?

811
00:41:28,936 --> 00:41:29,976
Yes, Madam.

812
00:41:30,215 --> 00:41:31,456
I do need your help.

813
00:41:31,776 --> 00:41:32,575
Let me tell you.

814
00:41:33,095 --> 00:41:34,816
People have been talking a lot

815
00:41:35,215 --> 00:41:37,735
that Yuehai Town Hospital is finished.

816
00:41:38,175 --> 00:41:39,695
It's quite large

817
00:41:40,055 --> 00:41:41,776
and has advanced equipment, right?

818
00:41:42,575 --> 00:41:44,215
Madam, you've heard about it?

819
00:41:44,376 --> 00:41:44,776
Yes.

820
00:41:44,936 --> 00:41:45,535
That's right.

821
00:41:45,695 --> 00:41:48,456
Yuehai's hospital just opened, so...

822
00:41:49,175 --> 00:41:51,336
Waiter, please.

823
00:41:52,535 --> 00:41:52,976
Hello.

824
00:41:53,095 --> 00:41:53,936
I'd like to ask.

825
00:41:53,976 --> 00:41:57,095
Is this called
the "Whole Roast Chicken"?

826
00:41:57,456 --> 00:41:58,016
Yes.

827
00:41:58,376 --> 00:42:00,936
Are you sure this is one whole chicken?

828
00:42:01,735 --> 00:42:02,615
Isn't it?

829
00:42:03,215 --> 00:42:03,856
Look.

830
00:42:04,615 --> 00:42:08,735
The metacarpal and shoulder bones
on each side are different sizes.

831
00:42:09,135 --> 00:42:10,456
And these drumsticks,

832
00:42:10,535 --> 00:42:12,135
one's bigger, one's smaller.

833
00:42:12,336 --> 00:42:14,735
This chicken's been pieced together.

834
00:42:16,215 --> 00:42:17,735
Shall I call the manager over?

835
00:42:17,816 --> 00:42:18,856
I'm not finished yet.

836
00:42:19,175 --> 00:42:21,135
This dish, the vinegar-braised cabbage.

837
00:42:21,575 --> 00:42:22,535
This dish

838
00:42:22,575 --> 00:42:24,416
is sweet but not sour.

839
00:42:24,896 --> 00:42:29,416
It's all about the layers,
soy, sugar, and vinegar, in that order.

840
00:42:29,816 --> 00:42:31,175
Tell your head chef.

841
00:42:31,535 --> 00:42:32,776
His skills need improvement.

842
00:42:33,816 --> 00:42:36,296
I'll order the whole chicken
every time I come.

843
00:42:36,376 --> 00:42:38,655
Next time, don't serve one like this.

844
00:42:38,735 --> 00:42:39,376
Right.

845
00:42:39,535 --> 00:42:40,896
Well, my mom's a food connoisseur.

846
00:42:40,976 --> 00:42:42,776
Just make it better next time.

847
00:42:42,976 --> 00:42:43,376
